福茂唱片音樂股份有限公司（ Linfair Records Ltd. ）由創辦人張人鳳先生成立於 1961 年，並於同一年取得世界最大古典音樂廠牌之一 -- Decca 的台灣區代理權。  1992 年，當時的 Decca 母公司 - 國際寶麗金唱片集團（ Polygram International ）買入百分之六十福茂股權，福茂唱片也同時加入了國際寶麗金唱片集團，福茂唱片的英文名稱因此改為 Decca Records Taiwan Ltd.。 2002 年，張耕宇先生及張霄芸女士向國際環球唱片集團（由於寶麗金唱片已於 1998 年被環球併購）買回其擁有的百分之六十福茂股權，福茂唱片又再度回到了100% 的獨立唱片公司，而英文名字又改回最初的 Linfair Records Ltd.。  雖然脫離了環球，但福茂仍然繼續在台代理 Decca。另外，福茂唱片還代理美國高音質獨立廠牌 Chesky 以及許多歐洲獨立廠牌.  福茂唱片除了代理國外廠牌外，於 1986 年開始發展國語流行歌曲，先後捧紅了許多台灣本地及香港、大陸地區的歌手，例如庾澄慶、邰正宵、林隆璇、黃舒駿、王菲、那英、范曉萱、王力宏、蘇永康、陳慧琳、許志安、周蕙 ... 等．近年福茂仍然繼續大力在國語歌曲市場發展，除了簽入高知名度藝人歌手外，也不斷培養全新歌手．近年成功推出的歌手藝人有范瑋琪、韋禮安、陳妍希、郭靜、張韶涵、曾沛慈、吳汶芳、畢書盡、朱俐靜、陳勢安、曾靜玟、陳彥允、李玉璽、法蘭黛樂團、李唯楓、王笠人 ... 等歌手。  福茂唱片的位置：http://goo.gl/zpRbSN

FACEBOOK https://www.facebook.com/ZeusTheServal  EMAIL TO BE REACHED: ZeusTheServal@gmail.com (PROFESSIONAL INQUIRIES ONLY!)  Zeus The Serval is an African Serval. The serval is a medium-sized cat going up to 40-55lbs. It is a strong yet slender animal with long legs and a fairly short tail. Due to its leg length it is relatively one of the tallest cats. Usually the serval is boldly spotted black on tawny with two or four stripes from the top of the head down the neck and back transitioning into spots. Servals have the longest legs of any cat relative to their body size.   ATTENTION: Servals DO NOT MAKE GOOD PETS. They are illegal in all but 4 states and require special permits to own.

column2: Relax My Dog - Relaxing Music for Dogs
column3: RelaxMyDog specialises in music designed for any breed of dog at any age.  The music is created for dogs who have anxiety problems or who are alone a lot and uses the power of music to calm and relax your pet.    It is perfect for those occasions which bring fireworks potentially scaring your pup or for a dog who suffers with separation anxiety.    The music uses sound sweep technology in order to capture your dog's attention and then combines lullaby-like melodies with classical music to keep your dog calm and soothed.  We have had great success with a number of fans' pets and will continue to bring you new music on a regular basis.  In the meantime please check in at our social media sites for lots of dog fun photos and more!  If you want to support us then you can do so through our Patreon page just take a look at our page and choose which tier suits you and thank you so very much for watching and giving! https://www.patreon.com/RelaxMyDog

I'm a wildlife educator with common exotic animals and one Canada Lynx. All are ambassadors educating the public. I possess a federal and state license to exhibit and educate with these animals. My videos are either training videos with Max in the beginning or just fun videos of my animals. Please understand that Max is comfortable on a leash. It allows me the opportunity to bring him out of his exhibit cage during educational presentations. This is a safe way for him to receive enrichment on our property.    I often hear "wild animals belong in the wild." What happens when there is no "wild" left? When the wild is gone there are two options: captivity or extinction. Education is the key to our species survival and the protection of our environment  Just to be clear my lynx is captive bred and can never be released into the wild.  Also please be aware that ALL comments are moderated. Clean comments please.
